data.description: Move in ready! Howard school district! All brick 4br/2ba, one level home with fenced backyard & outbuilding in established neighborhood! Fresh paint in most rooms. Open kitchen/breakfast area with solid surface countertops & 2 pantries. Refrigerator, washer & dryer stay! Two living areas & separate dining room. Vaulted, beamed ceilings in family room. Spacious primary bedroom with walk-in closet & private bathroom. Friends & family gatherings will be enjoyed under covered patio overlooking fenced backyard. Convenient to schools, shopping & I-75!
